element_texts.text:
The Lambs

Embossment                                                                                                                            130 WEST 44TH STREET

                                                                                                                                                          NEW YORK

Dear Connicks,

         How nice of you to send the prints. Will be out of town early in the week but if you come in after Wednesday do call me up at the above club in the 

morning

                    Sincerely
                 Sherwood Anderson

Embossment                                                                                                              The Lambs

                                                                                                                        130 WEST 44TH STREET
                                                                                                                                   NEW YORK

To
Charles & Mabel Connick

   I will be in New York at above address where a friend is putting me up -- for two or three weeks. If you are to be in town do let me know.
   It seems unlikely I shall get to Boston but if I do you may be sure I will eagerly accept your very kind invitation.
                              As Ever
                                    Sherwood
                                               Anderson
